Jarir Marketing Surges to Record High on Third-Quarter Dividend

-- B y   Z a h r a   H a n k i r
-- 
2011-10-18T08:27:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/jarir-marketing-surges-to-record-high-on-third-quarter-dividend.html
Jarir Marketing Co. (JARIR)  surged to a
record high as the largest Saudi retailer of stationery and
smartphones by market value recommended a third-quarter dividend
of 3.4 riyals and one bonus share for every two.  The shares surged 5.2 percent to 191.5 riyals, the highest
since July 2004, when Bloomberg started tracking the stock, at
11:18 a.m. in Riyadh trading.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zahra Hankir in Dubai at 
 zhankir@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Inal Ersan at 
 iersan@bloomberg.net  